'Excellent Long Raincoat.'
body: 'Stylish. Material is soft but sturdy. Leakproof. No water leakage from any seams. Hood with adjuster string. A belt provided to adjust at the waist though more belt loops could have been provided. Inside pocket for mobile. Overall a very good long raincoat. Recommended.'
